#X text 38 83 Actually \, much of what we see as a synthesis technique topic is actually in respect to a processing technique \, like with subtractive synthesis (which is processing the sound with a fulter). In the same way \, many effect processes are widely used in syhtesis (such as reverbs and whatnot). Hence \, there's only a fine line between synthesis techniques and audio processing.;
